        <h1>Meet Florence Price, the first Black woman to have her work premiered by a US orchestra</h1>
    
    
    
        <p class="publish_date">10 January 2024, 17:39</p>
    

    
<figure>
<img loading="lazy" alt="Florence Price had her work premiered by the Chicago Symphony Orchestra" class="content-image" data-image-catalogue-id="626668" width="660" height="370" src="https://imgs.classicfm.com/images/626668?crop=16_9&amp;width=660&amp;relax=1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=VgUMofSMiq00PvrVWMZ_i038Au8=" srcset="
                https://imgs.classicfm.com/images/626668?crop=16_9&amp;width=375&amp;relax=1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=NN2V4kiWHBa1EC6G_6TBn-B0kPU= 375w,
                https://imgs.classicfm.com/images/626668?crop=16_9&amp;width=420&amp;relax=1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=DHJWrf_l-ovnyXucFYEgUuPlhH4= 420w,
                https://imgs.classicfm.com/images/626668?crop=16_9&amp;width=660&amp;relax=1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=VgUMofSMiq00PvrVWMZ_i038Au8= 660w" sizes="
                (max-width: 375px) 375px,
                (max-width: 420px) 420px,
                660px" />
