<p class="paragraph-text"><strong>Read more: </strong><a href="https://www.classicfm.com/discover-music/black-composers-who-made-classical-music-history/"><strong>9 Black composers who changed the course of classical music history</strong></a></p>
<div class="video-container">
<div class="video-facade video-facade__brightcove" id="video_facade_brightcove_6344550332112" data-video-provider="brightcove" data-video-id="6344550332112" data-account="6057949401001">
